# pyshell
> A Shell class to exectue shell commands as object methods.


## Install

```
pip install bpyshell
```

## How to use

Import

```python
from pyshell.core import *
```

Create a shell object

```python
sh = Shell()
```

Call shell commands as object methods

```python
print(sh.ls())
```

